The LandSyMM-IMOGEN coupled model framework draws on, builds upon, and
re-distributes components developed by the broader Earth-system modelling
community. Each upstream component carries its own licence; this licence
applies only to the integrative work performed in this repository:

- The LPJ-GUESS modifications introduced for IMOGEN coupling
  (`lpjguess/modules/imogenoutput.cpp` and related additions)
- The Fortran IMOGEN ALLOCATABLE-array refactor
- The Python `imogen_ghg_controller` (the Intermediary Controller)
- The `tools/` adapter scripts and CMIP6 NetCDF converter
- The `scripts/` workstation/cluster launchers
- The unified documentation (`COUPLED_MODEL_INVESTIGATION.md`,
  `EXECUTION_PLAN.md`, `_phase2_findings/`, and the `docs/` tree)

For upstream components included in this distribution, see the LICENSE
file inside each component's directory:
- `lpjguess/LICENCE.TXT`     — LPJ-GUESS upstream licence (Lund University)
- `imogen/LICENSE`           — IMOGEN upstream licence
- `intermediary_py/LICENSE`  — MIT (matches this repository)

